== pcaprub-spox ==

This is a hacked version of pcaprub to
work on Ruby 1.9. You can find the original
here:

http://www.metasploit.com/svn/framework3/trunk/external/pcaprub

Depending on your distro, make sure the dev
packages are installed for libpcap. Install
is easy enough:

git clone git://github.com/spox/pcaprub-spox
cd pcaprub-spox
ruby extconf.rb
make
make install